33
00:02:53,970 --> 00:02:56,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（第忍话  忍与时间  其二）</font>

34
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:04,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我说汝啊  汝知道吾从南极大跳跃入湖时会发生些什么吗</font>

35
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:09,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  水会飞溅起来  湖里的水几乎全部都溅了起来</font>

36
00:03:10,110 --> 00:03:12,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后溅起又落下的水又会怎样呢</font>

37
00:03:12,950 --> 00:03:17,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">即使暂时会天空中飞舞  最后还是会受重力影响落到地面</font>

38
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">以「雨」的形态</font>

39
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:25,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当时这座湖周边受到长期日照  日照之强烈已造成地面干裂</font>

40
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:29,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我只是偶然地让那个地区下了场雨</font>

41
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:33,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从结果来看  吾不但拯救了许多条生命</font>

42
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:39,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">更是拯救了以湖周边为中心的一大片范围内的芸芸众生</font>

43
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:45,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后不巧的是  这个偶然的一刻居然就被目击到了</font>

44
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:50,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">偏偏就是这个「奇迹」发生的瞬间</font>

45
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:56,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说来汝啊  汝知道人类是怎么称呼「奇迹」的制造者吗</font>

46
00:03:57,660 --> 00:04:01,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对  奇迹的制造者被称为「神」</font>

47
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:08,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">正确地说  奇迹的制造者  无论是怪异还是人  都被视作「神」</font>

48
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:16,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">于是乎那座湖似乎就变成了什么信仰的对象</font>

49
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:24,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">周边的人们把那座湖作为「神之湖」来崇拜  来祈祷  也就是祈雨</font>

50
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:29,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在那些人看来  吾就是从湖里突然诞生出来的</font>

51
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:33,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就好像湖中的湖水变化成了吾的样子一样</font>

52
00:04:33,910 --> 00:04:38,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对当时的日本人来说  突然出现了这么个金发金眼身材修长的人物</font>

53
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:41,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也难怪他们把你当成神仙</font>

54
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:41,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（把小忍当成了神）</font>

55
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:42,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是）</font>

56
00:04:42,210 --> 00:04:42,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是……）</font>

57
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:46,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是那种状况肯定不会持续多久对吧</font>

58
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:47,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？为什么</font>

59
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个嘛…从你的性格考虑</font>

60
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:53,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你根本不是那种只是被敬仰信奉就满意的类型吧</font>

61
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为你是……</font>

62
00:04:53,970 --> 00:04:54,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（瞬息万变…）</font>

63
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:54,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（难以捉摸…）</font>

64
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:54,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（…的鬼）</font>

65
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:54,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（只有这一点不会改变的吸血鬼）</font>

66
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:59,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">正像汝所说的那样  这样的神仙生活并没有持续很久</font>

67
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:02,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">差不多将近一年吧</font>

68
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:08,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">且不说吾的性格  可以确定的是吾并不适合做神</font>

69
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:15,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺真宵就躺在我们的旁边  还没有恢复意识</font>

70
00:05:17,370 --> 00:05:21,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那些笨蛋们把吾当成神来祭祀的时候</font>

71
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:25,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾之所以那样顺水推舟  其实也因为正好想休息一下</font>

72
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:30,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不管怎么说都已经被当成神了  住所和食物也自不必愁</font>

73
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">感觉就像是度假一样</font>

74
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:39,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾的寝宫准确说是做出来的  就在那座消失了的湖泊的湖底</font>

75
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:44,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">换句话说就是建了个神社  建了个非常奢华的建筑</font>

76
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:50,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？汝说吾在这么贫困的村落里还要求人家建造神社</font>

77
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:51,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说吾是个无情的神？</font>

78
00:05:52,530 --> 00:05:53,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那可是吾自己建造的</font>

79
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:57,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">难道汝忘记了吗  吾那将物质实体化的能力</font>

80
00:05:57,820 --> 00:06:03,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且当时吾处于全盛期  建筑物及其附属一眨眼的工夫就做出来了</font>

81
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:08,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说汝啊  别就穿着一条内裤蹲在那边  吾都看不下去了</font>

82
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:10,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就给汝做件衣服汝快把它穿上好了</font>

83
00:06:12,050 --> 00:06:14,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  感觉不错  很合适很合适</font>

84
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:18,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾好歹也尽心尽责地做过神该做的工作</font>

85
00:06:18,890 --> 00:06:22,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且雨这种东西也不是下了一次就万事大吉的</font>

86
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:27,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾就每隔一段时间就降了几次雨  随便聚几朵乌云就降了</font>

87
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:30,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说惬意还确实蛮惬意舒服的</font>

88
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:34,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说是消磨时间倒不如说是享受时间</font>

89
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:41,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当时只是想着只要一直让人们「目击」到吾的话  存在力就能恢复</font>

90
00:06:42,490 --> 00:06:46,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然而令人遗憾的是  这并未能如愿</font>

91
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:55,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为吾并不是作为「吸血鬼」这种怪异被「目击」  当然是不会恢复的</font>

92
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:57,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾注意到这一点也花了不少时间</font>

93
00:06:58,340 --> 00:07:02,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实不作为吸血鬼被人目击也没什么关系</font>

94
00:07:02,930 --> 00:07:06,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">反正也不是火烧眉毛的问题</font>

95
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:09,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真正的问题在于吾是一直作为「神」被人「目击」的</font>

96
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和恶魔玩久了就会变成恶魔</font>

97
00:07:13,150 --> 00:07:16,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被叫做神叫久了就会变成神</font>

98
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:18,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一直没有主意到这一点的吾…</font>

99
00:07:18,740 --> 00:07:22,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  是对此一无所知的吾  真是太糊涂了</font>

100
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:26,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在想来  被当作神的状况吾根本就不应该去接受</font>

101
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:31,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在得知当地没有吸血鬼传说的时候就该赶紧走人</font>

102
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:39,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「一直假扮神明会遭到天谴」  可以单纯地就这样解释</font>

103
00:07:40,090 --> 00:07:42,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">至少那家伙是这么说的</font>

104
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:47,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那家伙  没错  就是吾的第一个眷属</font>

105
00:07:47,770 --> 00:07:50,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是妖刀心渡的持有者</font>

106
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:54,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个男人一直在战斗  就在那么和平的</font>

107
00:07:55,020 --> 00:07:59,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">某种意义上来说比现在还要和平的时代里  在战斗</font>

108
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝问吾和什么战斗？</font>

109
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:05,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果说他不会和人战斗的话  那么战斗的对象就十分有限了</font>

110
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  就是和怪异战斗</font>

111
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:14,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和怪异战斗？哎？也就是说他也是专家吗</font>

112
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:15,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不  不对）</font>

113
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:15,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（说是「战斗」总觉得哪里不对）</font>

114
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:15,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（倒不如说是）</font>

115
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:17,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（历/结论）</font>

116
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吸血鬼猎人</font>

117
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:19,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吧  就是那么回事</font>

118
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:23,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">以消灭妖怪为职业血缘正统的嫡系一族的末裔…</font>

119
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:27,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾也不记得他是不是这么说的了</font>

120
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:32,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">到这儿差不多该把第一个眷属的名字说出来了吧</font>

121
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:35,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">否则我根本无法想象他的样子</font>

122
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:40,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾哪知道  吾本来就对人间界的专有名词记忆模糊</font>

123
00:08:40,990 --> 00:08:42,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且也不会去叫谁的名字</font>

124
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:43,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这也太冷血了吧）</font>

125
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:44,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（铁血）</font>

126
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:44,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（热血）</font>

127
00:08:44,530 --> 00:08:44,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（都去哪里了）</font>

128
00:08:44,990 --> 00:08:51,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾一直叫那家伙「怪异杀手」  就像现在人们这么称呼吾那样</font>

129
00:08:52,210 --> 00:08:55,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为他拿着刀很容易和别人区分开来</font>

130
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:58,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且他还有专家所特有的气质</font>

131
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:03,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么为了方便起见就叫他「初代怪异杀手」吧</font>

132
00:09:03,260 --> 00:09:03,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（初代怪异杀手）</font>

133
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:03,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（第一个眷属）</font>

134
00:09:06,180 --> 00:09:11,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然是消灭妖怪的专家的话  可以理解成是来消灭你的吧</font>

135
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:16,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从某处听到了你的传言  特意过来解决你</font>

136
00:09:16,610 --> 00:09:20,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  不是的不是的  虽然有过一次战斗</font>

137
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:24,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是那家伙可不是为了消灭吾而来的</font>

138
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:32,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">想想看  他所听到的传言  也应该是吾被当做神明来祭拜的故事</font>

139
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">根本不是应该被消灭的对象</font>

140
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:39,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那家伙只是姑且先来看看情况</font>

141
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:43,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">湖泊突然间消失的同时并有神明显灵</font>

142
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:48,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">听到了这种事情  身为「血缘正统」的他  怎会坐视不理呢</font>

143
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:52,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说来那家伙是坐着轿子来的</font>

144
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:58,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">随从浩浩荡荡地跟在后面  宛如大名的队伍那般阵势</font>

145
00:09:58,520 --> 00:10:04,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从轿子下来的男人带着的一长一短两把刀吸引了吾的注意力</font>

146
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">长的一把就是妖刀「心渡」</font>

147
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:10,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝用过的那把就是它的复制品</font>

148
00:10:10,990 --> 00:10:15,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">第二把妖刀  那把小太刀的名字叫「梦渡」</font>

149
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:17,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那把小太刀究竟是怎样的一把刀呢？</font>

150
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:23,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果说「心渡」是杀怪异的刀  那么小太刀就是用来杀人的吗</font>

151
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:26,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是那样的话  它不就只是一把刀而已嘛</font>

152
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那是「怪异医师」</font>

153
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:28,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（怪异杀手）</font>

154
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:32,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小太刀「梦渡」是让怪异复生的刀</font>

155
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（怪异医师）</font>

156
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:29,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无论什么样的刀　都无法割离它们）</font>

157
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:38,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">让本来没有生命的怪异复生  这说起来也有些奇怪</font>

158
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:41,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之这就是一把让怪异复生的刀</font>

159
00:10:42,690 --> 00:10:46,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在那之后那家伙就定期地来巡视</font>

160
00:10:46,190 --> 00:10:49,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和吾说些话就回去了  如此反复</font>

161
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:56,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾也帮助过他消灭过一些妖怪  也就在那时建立了信任关系</font>

162
00:10:56,910 --> 00:11:01,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说小忍  既然这样你倒不如就这么成为神明不也挺好的嘛</font>

163
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:06,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">听你说来  你倒也是那样的人才  非常的合适</font>

164
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:14,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也不虐待百姓  要说有问题的话  就是你的吸血冲动了吧</font>

165
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:14,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（小忍  声音/台词）</font>

166
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:18,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">白痴  有那个吸血冲动的问题就已经足够了</font>

167
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:20,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真是顽固啊）</font>

168
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:24,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再说了  问题还不止那些</font>

169
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:30,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾身为怪异  吾身为吸血鬼这个存在本身就是问题</font>

170
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:38,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾身为怪异  姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心的存在  会聚集怪异</font>

171
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:44,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且聚集过来的  比起怪异更多的是构不成怪异的负能量</font>

172
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:46,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是所谓的「不好的东西」</font>

173
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:49,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是的  是吾大意了</font>

174
00:11:50,130 --> 00:11:57,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾不能在一块地方停留太久  因为会打破该地区怪异的生态平衡</font>

175
00:11:58,270 --> 00:12:05,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">之所以这样都怪之前住在南极这个人类和怪异都不存在的地方</font>

176
00:12:06,020 --> 00:12:11,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个地方根本不会聚集「不好的东西」  而吾却完全没有注意到</font>

177
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:15,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">注意到事情发生的是附近的居民</font>

178
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:17,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">传闻是这样的</font>

179
00:12:17,490 --> 00:12:18,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「人消失了」</font>

180
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:19,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「人不见了」）</font>

181
00:12:19,450 --> 00:12:21,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「出去了就再也没回来」</font>

182
00:12:21,330 --> 00:12:21,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「不见了踪影」）</font>

183
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:26,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然吾和初代怪异杀手讨论过  也一起搜查过</font>

184
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:32,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果却因为没有任何证据  于是便归结于可能是人类犯下的罪行</font>

185
00:12:33,340 --> 00:12:35,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就不是吾等的工作了</font>

186
00:12:35,140 --> 00:12:35,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不是「神」和「专家」的工作）</font>

187
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:37,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是警察的工作</font>

188
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:37,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（得出了这样的结论）</font>

189
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:40,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之  吾什么都没做</font>

190
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:42,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是居民还是不断地消失</font>

191
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:46,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">附近的居民还是不断地下落不明</font>

192
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:50,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">直到一个人也不剩为止</font>

193
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:58,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">呃  「一个人都不剩」指的是什么呢</font>

194
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从你的语气和说话方式中</font>

195
00:13:01,410 --> 00:13:05,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我只能理解成周边的居民都不见了</font>

196
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是这样</font>

197
00:13:07,290 --> 00:13:10,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">整个村子的人都失踪了</font>

198
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:10,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（规模太大了）</font>

199
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:10,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（实在是）</font>

200
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（究竟有多少人失踪了啊？）</font>

201
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:14,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">接下来吾走遍了周围所有的村子</font>

202
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:14,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吗</font>

203
00:13:15,430 --> 00:13:18,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后通过这次探索吾发现</font>

204
00:13:18,890 --> 00:13:22,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">周围的村子也都一个人也不剩了</font>

205
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如同划好了界线一般</font>

206
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:29,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从某处开始  之外的村子都平安无事</font>

207
00:13:29,270 --> 00:13:29,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（界线）</font>

208
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">界线</font>

209
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:29,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（意大利语：界线）</font>

210
00:13:29,570 --> 00:13:29,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（界线）</font>

211
00:13:29,650 --> 00:13:29,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（德语：界线）</font>

212
00:13:29,730 --> 00:13:29,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（葡萄牙语：界线）</font>

213
00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:29,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（俄语：界线）</font>

214
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:29,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（西班牙语：界线）</font>

215
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:30,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（分界）</font>

216
00:13:30,780 --> 00:13:36,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说划分界线的根据就是有没有信奉你吗</font>

217
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:39,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  分得再准确一点的话</font>

218
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:42,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是以「知不知道吾」为界线</font>

219
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和信仰无关</font>

220
00:13:43,370 --> 00:13:43,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有人的村子）</font>

221
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:43,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（空无一人的村子）</font>

222
00:13:43,710 --> 00:13:43,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（——她）</font>

223
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:47,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后吾终于注意到了</font>

224
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:51,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">尽管吾长期停留在这里</font>

225
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:54,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但负面能量却完全没有积攒起来</font>

226
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要是说有原因的话</font>

227
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:59,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾想肯定是因为吾在这里停留了太久</font>

228
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:03,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个负面能量已经在某个地方引发了什么事件吧</font>

229
00:14:03,430 --> 00:14:05,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但吾在周围转了一圈</font>

230
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:06,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">却并没有发现类似的事件</font>

231
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:09,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没有发生这种事件</font>

232
00:14:09,230 --> 00:14:11,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这一点很奇怪  十分异常</font>

233
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">绝对是异常状态</font>

234
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:14,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说实话  对于吾来说</font>

235
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:17,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">比起周围的居民全都消失了这件事</font>

236
00:14:17,910 --> 00:14:22,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾更为周围没有聚集起任何东西这件事而感到不可思议</font>

237
00:14:22,540 --> 00:14:23,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">甚至有些感到恐怖</font>

238
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:29,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为感到恐怖  所以吾就回家睡觉了</font>

239
00:14:30,340 --> 00:14:30,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">喂</font>

240
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:34,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎？  不舒服的时候最好的办法不就是老老实实地睡觉吗</font>

241
00:14:34,710 --> 00:14:35,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然确实是这样！</font>

242
00:14:36,090 --> 00:14:36,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（竹○○（割爱））（原文是哆拉A梦里的竹蜻蜓）</font>

243
00:14:36,090 --> 00:14:40,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后  正当吾忘了个一干二净准备去睡回笼觉的时候</font>

244
00:14:40,930 --> 00:14:43,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">妨碍吾睡觉的家伙却出现了</font>

245
00:14:43,850 --> 00:14:44,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">出现了是指…</font>

246
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:46,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">敌人出现了吗</font>

247
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:45,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（敌人）</font>

248
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:45,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（敌人）</font>

249
00:14:45,770 --> 00:14:45,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（法语：敌人）</font>

250
00:14:45,850 --> 00:14:45,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（意大利语：敌人）</font>

251
00:14:45,930 --> 00:14:46,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（德语：敌人）</font>

252
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:46,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（西班牙语：敌人）</font>

253
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:46,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（俄语：敌人）</font>

254
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:46,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「黑暗」）</font>

255
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是的</font>

256
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:50,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">出现的是「初代怪异杀手」</font>

257
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:56,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所谓的新情报是关于怪异杀手部下的</font>

258
00:14:56,780 --> 00:14:58,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他们也都消失了</font>

259
00:14:58,570 --> 00:15:00,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不知道消失到什么地方去了</font>

260
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:04,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">等初代怪异杀手回过神来他已经变成孤身一人了</font>

261
00:15:05,450 --> 00:15:08,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">于是听了他的描述之后</font>

262
00:15:06,830 --> 00:15:07,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（他和吾不同）</font>

263
00:15:08,210 --> 00:15:08,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（很有危机感）</font>

264
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「那就不得不调查一下了呢」</font>

265
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（而且比危机感更强烈的）</font>

266
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:11,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（是恐惧感）</font>

267
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:12,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾用一副认真的表情这么说道</font>

268
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:17,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然吾已经在周围的村子转了一圈掌握了现状</font>

269
00:15:17,970 --> 00:15:22,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但吾还是陪同初代怪异杀手再次调查了各个村子</font>

270
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当然村子的状况没有任何变化</font>

271
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:29,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">失踪的人们并没有突然间回来</font>

272
00:15:30,690 --> 00:15:32,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">事情就是在这不凑巧的时候发生的</font>

273
00:15:32,690 --> 00:15:32,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（突然）</font>

274
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:33,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（出现了）</font>

275
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:35,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾们调查了最后一个村子</font>

276
00:15:35,530 --> 00:15:39,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当确认最后一间房子里也没有人后</font>

277
00:15:39,650 --> 00:15:42,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初代怪异杀手真是要多消沉有多消沉</font>

278
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:45,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就在他纤细的心灵受到伤害的时候</font>

279
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:47,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那东西出现了</font>

280
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:50,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是汝所说的「黑暗」</font>

281
00:15:51,210 --> 00:15:52,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">毫无征兆地</font>

282
00:15:52,830 --> 00:15:54,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在大白天就出现了</font>

283
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:55,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（终于出现了）</font>

284
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:56,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（进入正题了）</font>

285
00:15:57,460 --> 00:16:00,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说实话  吾一开始还以为那是什么自然现象</font>

286
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:06,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说吾觉得用「黑色的一团」来描述是最合适的</font>

287
00:16:06,970 --> 00:16:10,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但它似乎又并没有「团结」成「一团」的样子</font>

288
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被吞了进去</font>

289
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:14,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾们两个都被吞了进去</font>

290
00:16:14,860 --> 00:16:16,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就是那些人消失的原因吗</font>

291
00:16:17,070 --> 00:16:19,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当吾发现的时候已经太迟了</font>

292
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:22,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾全身上下大约四分之三都已经被吞了进去</font>

293
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:27,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过留下四分之一也够了</font>

294
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:28,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">足够用来逃跑了</font>

295
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:31,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾一路飞到了南极</font>

296
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:30,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（啊  这不是在逃跑  这不是在逃跑）</font>

297
00:16:31,410 --> 00:16:31,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（吾有生以来）</font>

298
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:32,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（从来没有逃跑过）</font>

299
00:16:32,330 --> 00:16:37,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算是吾  也是第一次在肉体上受到如此大的损伤</font>

300
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:39,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之吾想和它保持距离</font>

301
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:41,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但从结果上来说</font>

302
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:43,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实没必要做到这一步</font>

303
00:16:44,180 --> 00:16:46,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为那片「黑暗」并没有追过来</font>

304
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:48,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不管吾等了多久</font>

305
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:52,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就这样吾离开了日本</font>

306
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:54,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后就再也没有回来</font>

307
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:59,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾再次到访日本便要追溯到半年前</font>

308
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:03,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并且在那时遇到了汝</font>

309
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？  等一下</font>

310
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:08,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初代怪异杀手最后怎么样了</font>

311
00:17:09,450 --> 00:17:10,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾不是说了吗</font>

312
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:13,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他和吾一起被「黑暗」吞噬了</font>

313
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:15,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾只被吞噬了四分之三</font>

314
00:17:15,580 --> 00:17:19,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但先被吞进去的他可就不止这样了</font>

315
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">几乎全身都被吞进去了</font>

316
00:17:21,670 --> 00:17:22,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这不是很奇怪吗  小忍</font>

317
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:26,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果那家伙在当时就被「黑暗」给吞掉了的话</font>

318
00:17:26,390 --> 00:17:28,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那故事不就结束了吗</font>

319
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:30,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不不  不是这样的</font>

320
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:31,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">认真听吾说啊</font>

321
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:36,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾说的可是「他几乎整个人都被吞进去了」</font>

322
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:37,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊</font>

323
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:40,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以我才会有疑问啊  那不就…</font>

324
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:40,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">几乎</font>

325
00:17:40,860 --> 00:17:42,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说还留下了一部分</font>

326
00:17:44,110 --> 00:17:45,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">右手腕留了下来</font>

327
00:17:46,910 --> 00:17:47,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">手腕？</font>

328
00:17:47,820 --> 00:17:50,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾不是说了他是先被吞进去的吗</font>

329
00:17:50,580 --> 00:17:51,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后当他被吞没的时候</font>

330
00:17:51,910 --> 00:17:56,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他简直如同抓住救命稻草一般抓住了吾的手腕</font>

331
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像这样紧紧地</font>

332
00:18:00,050 --> 00:18:04,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾和他的手腕一起飞去了南极</font>

333
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:11,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果被留在南极的就只有吾一个人和他的手腕</font>

334
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:13,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">留下的…</font>

335
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:15,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是孤零零的一个吾</font>

336
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:18,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">时隔百年  吾又一次有了这种感觉</font>

337
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:22,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾被巨大的孤独感所包围</font>

338
00:18:22,530 --> 00:18:28,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这和吾刚刚遭遇了「黑暗」这一未知现象也是有关系的</font>

339
00:18:29,490 --> 00:18:32,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说不至于感到危险和不安</font>

340
00:18:32,370 --> 00:18:33,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但至少吾感受到了威胁</font>

341
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:36,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以吾让他复活了</font>

342
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:39,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾造出了第一个眷属</font>

343
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:42,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是有种说法叫做「吊桥效应」吗</font>

344
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:45,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">人会把身在吊桥上时因恐惧而加速的心跳</font>

345
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:49,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">误认为是坠入爱河所产生的心动</font>

346
00:18:50,180 --> 00:18:50,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说</font>

347
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:51,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（如果这么解释的话）</font>

348
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:53,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当身处吊桥上或者其他环境下</font>

349
00:18:52,850 --> 00:18:53,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（的确是一种很容易理解的现象）</font>

350
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:56,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">生命受到威胁的时候</font>

351
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:54,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不过那个「效果」）</font>

352
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:56,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也可以有其他解释）</font>

353
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:58,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">生物就会本能地想要留下后代</font>

354
00:18:58,480 --> 00:19:00,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因而会容易坠入爱河之类</font>

355
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:04,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">恋情还是爱情  家人或是眷属</font>

356
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那并不是这些感情所导致的现象</font>

357
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:08,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是有着冲动性的</font>

358
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:08,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（汝可以表现得失望一点）</font>

359
00:19:08,530 --> 00:19:10,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无法被赞赏的理由</font>

360
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:09,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（在这里）</font>

361
00:19:11,370 --> 00:19:12,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是因为心灵变得脆弱了而已</font>

362
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:18,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾大口地咬在那家伙的右手腕上  吸了他的血</font>

363
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:22,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是为了进食  而是为了制造眷属吸了他的血</font>

364
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:24,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为讨厌孤独</font>

365
00:19:25,260 --> 00:19:26,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以吾放弃了神的身份</font>

366
00:19:26,840 --> 00:19:28,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">做回了吸血鬼</font>

367
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:39,440
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}今もずっとその声を覚えてるから</font>

368
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:39,440
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">现在我也记得你的声音</font>

369
00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:51,540
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日走った道に</font>

370
00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:51,540
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子走过的路</font>

371
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:54,360
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日見上げた空に</font>

372
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:54,360
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子仰望的天空</font>

373
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:59,610
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}二度と返らない時を重ねてる</font>

374
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:59,610
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">无法回去的曾经反复叠加</font>

375
00:20:00,170 --> 00:20:02,810
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}君は笑うだろうか</font>

376
00:20:00,170 --> 00:20:02,810
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你恐怕会笑我吧</font>

377
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:05,600
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}少し怒るだろうね</font>

378
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:05,600
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">会有一丝生气吧</font>

379
00:20:05,820 --> 00:20:11,330
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}こんな諦め悪い僕のことを</font>

380
00:20:05,820 --> 00:20:11,330
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">我就是这么一个无法死心的人</font>

381
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:15,020
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何度でも</font>

382
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:15,020
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">一次又一次</font>

383
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:20,960
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}迂闊に願う可能性を清書して  （いつまでも）</font>

384
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:20,960
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">将那些恍惚间许愿的可能性整理起来  （直到永远）</font>

385
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:25,530
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}まだ迷いそうに騙されてたくて</font>

386
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:25,530
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">都想这样迷茫地被自己所欺骗</font>

387
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:31,090
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だから「どうかせめて」なんて思う心は</font>

388
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:31,090
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此许下这些愿望的心情</font>

389
00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:34,580
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}一時的な感傷だって</font>

390
00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:34,580
