397
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:51,560
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}くれた日々に偽りなんてないと言ってあげよう</font>

398
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:51,560
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你曾给我带来的那些日子没有虚假</font>

399
00:20:53,250 --> 00:20:57,540
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}忘れないで</font>

400
00:20:53,250 --> 00:20:57,540
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">不要将我忘记</font>

401
00:21:03,180 --> 00:21:04,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  你成功了吗</font>

402
00:21:05,230 --> 00:21:06,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾失败了</font>

403
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:07,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">失…失败？</font>

404
00:21:07,970 --> 00:21:11,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和吾想的一样  初代怪异杀手复活了</font>

405
00:21:12,090 --> 00:21:16,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过  说不定是因为他的内心不如汝强大吧</font>

406
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:20,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在回想起来  说不定是因为吾关心的不够吧</font>

407
00:21:21,290 --> 00:21:25,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">记得你说他自己冲到了太阳下  化为灰烬了啊</font>

408
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:28,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  他自杀了</font>

409
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:28,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无法避免）</font>

410
00:21:28,140 --> 00:21:28,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没能避免）</font>

411
00:21:28,390 --> 00:21:28,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（他的自杀）</font>

412
00:21:28,990 --> 00:21:31,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这是大约九成的吸血鬼最终都会选择的</font>

413
00:21:31,950 --> 00:21:34,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">普通得不能再普通的死法…</font>

414
00:21:37,150 --> 00:21:37,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（燃烧  再生）</font>

415
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:37,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（燃烧  再生）</font>

416
00:21:37,900 --> 00:21:38,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（燃烧  再生）</font>

417
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:38,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（直到彻底化为灰烬为止）</font>

418
00:21:41,190 --> 00:21:43,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那时你没去救他吗</font>

419
00:21:43,930 --> 00:21:47,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像春假时你救了跑去太阳下的我那样</font>

420
00:21:48,050 --> 00:21:49,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾没法救他</font>

421
00:21:49,550 --> 00:21:54,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且当时的吾也不太明白他为什么要这么做</font>

422
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:59,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说回来  直到他选择自杀为止  吾还和他交流了很多</font>

423
00:21:59,940 --> 00:22:03,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过当时吾和他之间的关系已经几乎破裂了</font>

424
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:05,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这是无计可施的</font>

425
00:22:06,150 --> 00:22:06,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">破裂是指？</font>

426
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:07,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（答非所问）</font>

427
00:22:07,130 --> 00:22:07,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这简直是答非所问）</font>

428
00:22:07,580 --> 00:22:10,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说白了就是他生气了</font>

429
00:22:10,270 --> 00:22:14,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初代怪异杀手对于吾把他变成吸血鬼这件事生气了</font>

430
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:15,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（居然不是「神」而是「鬼」）</font>

431
00:22:15,850 --> 00:22:16,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「吸血鬼」的身份——暴露了）</font>

432
00:22:16,250 --> 00:22:18,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从一只断手上获得了新生</font>

433
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:23,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">重生为吸血鬼的初代怪异杀手</font>

434
00:22:23,500 --> 00:22:25,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对吾说的第一句话是</font>

435
00:22:25,510 --> 00:22:30,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「你这怪物  居然骗了我们」</font>

436
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:35,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他对吾怒吼道「这全都是你害的吗」</font>

437
00:22:35,330 --> 00:22:38,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说是怒吼  不如说更接近责问吧</font>

438
00:22:39,010 --> 00:22:42,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他甚至对吾说吾会受到天谴什么的</font>

439
00:22:42,740 --> 00:22:46,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说他把包括失踪在内的所有事情都怪罪到你头上了吗</font>

440
00:22:47,300 --> 00:22:49,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他甚至认为那片「黑暗」也是你动的手脚</font>

441
00:22:50,040 --> 00:22:50,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（规模不一样）</font>

442
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:52,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后你是怎么做的呢</font>

443
00:22:52,730 --> 00:22:53,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">先不管动机如何</font>

444
00:22:53,950 --> 00:22:55,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你毫无疑问是救了他一命</font>

445
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:59,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但却被他这么说  心里肯定不太好受吧</font>

446
00:22:59,370 --> 00:23:01,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  那倒没有</font>

447
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:04,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过要解开误会实在太麻烦了</font>

448
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:06,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以吾就随他说去了</font>

449
00:23:06,850 --> 00:23:11,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾想他虽然现在有些混乱  但一定很快就会冷静下来吧</font>

450
00:23:12,910 --> 00:23:13,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（要说不想让他死去的想法)</font>

451
00:23:13,070 --> 00:23:13,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真的）</font>

452
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:13,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（完全）</font>

453
00:23:13,370 --> 00:23:13,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（一丝都没有）</font>

454
00:23:13,530 --> 00:23:13,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（那是不可能的）</font>

455
00:23:14,870 --> 00:23:15,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这家伙要是那种女人的话）</font>

456
00:23:15,120 --> 00:23:15,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我就不会像这样活着了）</font>

457
00:23:15,490 --> 00:23:15,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不会作为半个吸血鬼——而活着）</font>

458
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:19,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但他并没有冷静下来</font>

459
00:23:19,230 --> 00:23:21,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">混乱  甚至精神错乱</font>

460
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:23,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与吾彻底翻脸</font>

461
00:23:23,430 --> 00:23:25,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">最终选择了自杀</font>

462
00:23:25,860 --> 00:23:28,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他一边对吾说着怨恨的话语</font>

463
00:23:28,380 --> 00:23:30,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其中还夹杂着后悔和抱怨</font>

464
00:23:30,950 --> 00:23:34,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后当着吾的面冲进了阳光下</font>

465
00:23:34,650 --> 00:23:35,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">——死了</font>

466
00:23:36,210 --> 00:23:37,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾既没能阻止他</font>

467
00:23:37,580 --> 00:23:38,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也没能救他</font>

468
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:42,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">明明在抵达南极后吾都把真名告诉他了</font>

469
00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:49,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果他只在临自杀前叫了吾「姬丝秀忒」一次</font>

470
00:23:51,470 --> 00:23:54,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">即使如此  他还是叫你「姬丝秀忒」</font>

471
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:57,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既不是「刃下心」  也不是「雅赛劳拉莉昂」</font>

472
00:23:58,510 --> 00:24:00,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是和我一样叫你「姬丝秀忒」</font>

473
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:01,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来…</font>

474
00:24:02,580 --> 00:24:04,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后他就死了</font>

475
00:24:04,610 --> 00:24:06,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为吸血鬼是不死之身</font>

476
00:24:06,710 --> 00:24:10,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以准确地说应该是「毁灭」了吧</font>

477
00:24:10,230 --> 00:24:11,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之他死了</font>

478
00:24:11,710 --> 00:24:17,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">作为遗物他留下了费尽全部心血打造的妖刀心渡的复制品</font>

479
00:24:17,910 --> 00:24:20,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">反正他是为了杀死吾才去打造的吧</font>

480
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:25,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">直到那时为止  吾只是无意中没有制造眷属而已</font>

481
00:24:25,410 --> 00:24:29,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并不是固执地坚持着单身主义</font>

482
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:34,050
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过当吾目送着他那冒着青色火焰的尸体逐渐消逝</font>

483
00:24:34,250 --> 00:24:36,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾就发誓再也不去制造眷属</font>

484
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:41,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再也不因摄取养分之外的目的去吸人血</font>

485
