<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说得好听点  我甚至无法佩服她</font>

488
00:24:49,610 --> 00:24:51,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为结果直到最终</font>

489
00:24:52,210 --> 00:24:55,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她无论是作为「神」还是「吸血鬼」</font>

490
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:58,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都无法和人类「好好相处」</font>

491
00:25:00,010 --> 00:25:01,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这段鬼的独白</font>

492
00:25:01,820 --> 00:25:04,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">距今四百年前的故事</font>

