00:25:17,850 --> 00:25:19,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之先把斧乃木妹妹拉进来再说</font>

504
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:20,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">预告篇Quiz！</font>

505
00:25:20,900 --> 00:25:21,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">Quiz！</font>

506
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:23,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">『奥兹国历险记』  读过没有啊？</font>

507
00:25:23,150 --> 00:25:31,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}好厉害！快给我们看看！</font>

508
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:25,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">读过读过  都快读烂了</font>

509
00:25:25,650 --> 00:25:28,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一起旅行的伙伴不是狮子稻草人和铁皮机器人么</font>

510
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错啊  传说中的御三家啊</font>

511
