522
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">下集  鬼物语  第三话</font>

523
00:25:50,780 --> 00:25:52,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">忍与时间  其三</font>

524
00:25:51,600 --> 00:26:00,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}没有成神</font>

525
00:25:51,600 --> 00:26:00,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}成佛了！</font>

526
00:25:52,330 --> 00:25:54,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来真应该好好推敲一下队长的设定了</font>

